{"tid":2506210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府修例「完善」選舉制度 覆核王郭卓堅入稟挑戰 高院指屬人大決定無權覆核其合憲性 拒絕受理","createTime":"2021-04-27T07:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T08:25:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f670ba4fa559b37051f7177ddacd9c16c9a6c50","tid":2506210,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"聲稱「完善」香港選舉制度的修例草案本月初在立法會首讀及二讀，覆核王郭卓堅上周入稟高等法院，指特首林鄭月娥提交草案違反《基本法》及程序公義，令高度自治「突然死亡」，提出司法覆核。高等法院今頒下判詞，拒絕受理覆核申請，直指有關決定是根據《基本法》附件一及附件二而訂，沒有基礎挑戰其合憲性；而終審法院在黎智英涉國安法一案中，亦裁定本港法院無權覆核人大決定是否違憲，故認為是次覆核沒有合理爭辯或勝訴機會。<br />\n<br />\n覆核答辯人是特首林鄭月娥，利害關係方為政制及內地事務局長曾國衛。郭卓堅指，特首向立法會提交《2021年完善候選制度（綜合修訂）條例草案》，違反《人權法》保障的選舉權；選委會中直選產生的區議會議席，被由政府委任的多個委員會所取代，國安處亦參與審核特首候選人資格，造成利益衝突。<br />\n<br />\n高等法院原訟庭法官周家明在判詞中表示，人大常委會於3月11日通過《完善香港特別行政區選舉制度決定》，並於同月31日通過經修訂的《基本法》附件一及附件二。由於條例草案是根據修訂後的附件提出，故申請人並沒有挑戰其合憲性的基礎。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在黎智英涉嫌違反港區國安法一案中，終審法院法官一致認為，由於港區國安法是根據人大決定而作出，並以納入《基本法》附件三的形式立法，故本港法庭無權覆核其合憲性。同樣地，法庭亦無權挑戰人大的3.11及3.31決定是否違憲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/XGZUY2OJIZE3ZBH23Z7DONFPCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FXGZUY2OJIZE3ZBH23Z7DONFPCY%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=51d954f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FXGZUY2OJIZE3ZBH23Z7DONFPCY%2F&h=b0a07ebf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/XGZUY2OJIZE3ZBH23Z7DONFPCY/</a>"},{"pid":"12ebfa32c3799011bf3ed235984980ac404f7589","tid":2506210,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6faa94ff5a44d684e16273e95bc9ef611195bbed","tid":2506210,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:18:02.000Z","msg":"返台灣啦,香港好危險"},{"pid":"e6f53520f9bc68c18608fc381314071514268579","tid":2506210,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d0af163388930249c85d1ad665fef49246488ec","tid":2506210,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626b3f3e3c315545affb13625520090b71e0c5b5","tid":2506210,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"法院都無權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c319b6fe59d2ebda18036f82fd0c3058a47462","tid":2506210,"uid":26154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"626b3f3e3c315545affb13625520090b71e0c5b5","tid":2506210,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"法院都無權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"CFA訂左案例，佢一日無新案例推翻一日高院都要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />焗住要啲人打到上終院(仲要無乜可能贏)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047c311dd8115161d8f14f0907f1341b9572ced6","tid":2506210,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"626b3f3e3c315545affb13625520090b